            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the physical state of wired-tired: body alert, mind exhausted, no crossover point. Use in bed or just before. The script targets the physical layer — the restlessness, the held muscles, the breath that won't slow down."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
